quran[86]{c,v,t}:
  78,1,Yeh log kis chez kay bary mein poch gach ker rahy hein
  78,2,Us bari khabar kay mutaliq
  78,3,Jiss kay bary mein yeh ikhtylaf ker rahay hein
  78,4,Yaqenan yeh abhi jan lein gay
  78,5,Phir bil yaqeen inhein buhat jald maloom hojaey ga
  78,6,kiya hum nay zameen ko farsh nahi banaya
  78,7,Aur paharon ko mikhein(nahi banaya)
  78,8,Aur hum nay tumhein jora jora paida kiya
  78,9,Aur hum nay tumhari nend ko aram ka sabab banaya
  78,10,Aur rat ko hum nay parda banaya hay
  78,11,Aur din ko hum nay waqat e rozgar banaya
  78,12,Aur tumhary opper hum nay 7 masboot asman banaey
  78,13,Aur ik chamkta howa roshan chiragh(soraj)paida kiya
  78,14,Aur badlon say hum nay bakasrat bhyta hoa pani barsaya
  78,15,Atky us say anaj or sabza ugaein
  78,16,Aur ghanay bagh(bhi ugay)
  78,17,be-shak faislay kay din ka waqat mukarer hay
  78,18,Jiss din kay sor mein phonka jaey ga phir tum foj der foj chaly ao gay
  78,19,Aur asman khol diaya jaey ga to is mein darwazy darwazy hojaein gay
  78,20,Aur pahar chaly jaein gay pus wo sarab hojaein gay
  78,21,Be-shak dozakh ghat mein hay
  78,22,sarkashon ka thikana wohi hay
  78,23,Is mein wo mudaton tak pary rahein gay
  78,24,Na kabhi is mein khunki ka maza chakein gay na pani ka
  78,25,Siwaey garm pani aur(beyti)peep kay
  78,26,(Unko)pora pora badla milay ga
  78,27,Unhein to hisab ki tawaqa hi na thi
  78,28,Aur bebaki say hamari ayton ki takzeb kerty thy
  78,29,Hum nay her ik chez ko likh ker shumar ker rakah hay
  78,30,Ab tum(apnay kiey ka )maza chako hum tumhara azab bhi barhaty rahein gay
  78,31,Yaqeenan perhezgar logon kay liey kamyabi hay
  78,32,Baghat hein or angoor hay
  78,33,Aur nojawan kunwari hum omer auratein hein
  78,34,Aur chalkty hoy jam sharab hein
  78,35,Wahan na to who byhoda batein sunein gay aur na jhoti batein sunein gay
  78,36,(Unko) tery rab ki taraf say (unkay nek amal ka)yeh badla milay ga jo kafi inam hoga
  78,37,(Is rab ki taraf say milay ga jo kay)asmano ka aur zameen ka aur jo kuch in kay dermiyan hay inka perwardigar hay aur bari bakhsish kernay wala hay kisi ko is say bat chet kerney ka ikhtyar nahi hoga
  78,38,Jiss din roh or faristy safein bandh ker khary hongay to koi kalam na kersakay ga magar jis say rehman ijazat dayday aur wo thek bat zaban say nikalay
  78,39,Yeh din haq hay ab jo chaeiy apnay rab kay pass (nek amal kerkay) thikana banalein
  78,40,Hum nay tumhein unqareeb anay walay azab say dara diya(aur chokanna ker diya) hai. jis din insan apnay haton ki kamai ko dekh ly gaur kafir kahy ga kay kash!mein mitti hojata
  79,1,Doob ker sakhti say khenchnay walon ki qasam
  79,2,Band khol ker chora dyney walon ki qasam
  79,3,Aur terney phirnay walon ki qasam
  79,4,Phir dor ker agy barhnay walon ki qasam
  79,5,Phir kam ki tadbeer kernay walon ki qasam
  79,6,Jis din kanpney wali kanpe gi
  79,7,Us ky bad ik peechy aney wali (peechy peechy) aye gi
  79,8,(buhat se)dil us din dharakty hongy
  79,9,Gin ki nigahen nichi hongien
  79,10,kehty hein ke kiya hum pehli ki si halat ki taraf phir lot aye jaein gay
  79,11,Kiya us waqt jab ke hum bosida hadiyaan hojaein gay
  79,12,Kehty hein ke phir to ye lotna nuksandeh hay
  79,13,(maloom hona chaiey)wo to sirf ik (khufnak)dant hay
  79,14,Kay (jis kay zihar hoty hi )wo ik dam medan mein jama hojaein gay
  79,15,Kiya Musa (aleh e salam)ki khabar tumhein phunchi hay
  79,16,Jabkay unhein unkay rab nay pak medan TUA mein pukara
  79,17,(kay)tum firoon kay pass jao unsay sirkashi ikhtyar kerli hay
  79,18,ussy kaho kay kiya to apnai durstagi or islah chata hy
  79,19,Aur yeh ky mein tujhhy terey Rab ki rah dikhata takay tu (uss say) darnay lagy
  79,20,Pus ussay bari nishani dikhai
  79,21,To us ney jhutlaya aur na fermani ki
  79,22,Phir palta dor dhoop kertay huye
  79,23,Phir sabb ko jama kerty pukaara
  79,24,Tum sab ka rab mein hi hun
  79,25,To(sab say buland o baala)) Allah ney bhi usay aakhrat ky aur duneya ky azab mein giriftaar kerliya
  79,26,Be-shak is mein is shaks kay liye ibrat hy jo daray
  79,27,Kiya tumhara peda kerna zadadushwar hy ya aasman ka
  79,28,Iss ki bulandi unchi ki phir issay theek thak kerdia
  79,29,Is ski raat ko tareek banaya aur iss kay din ko nikala
  79,30,Aur is kay baad zameen ko (humwaar)bicha diya
  79,31,Iss mein say paani aur chaara nikala
  79,32,Aur paharon ko (mazboot) ghar diya
  79,33,Yeh sab tumhary aur tumhary janwaron kay fiady kat liey (hein)
  79,34,Aur jab wo bari afat(qiyamat) ayegi
  79,35,Jiss din kay insan apnay kiey hoy kamon ko yad kery ga
  79,36,Aur (her)dekhney waly kay samaney jahanum zahir ki jaey gi
  79,37,To jiss(shaks) nay sarkashi ki (hogi)
  79,38,Aur duneyawi zindagi ko tarjeeh di(hogi)
  79,39,(uska)thikana jahanum hi hay
  79,40,Han jo shaks apnay rab kay samaney khara honay say darta raha hogaaur apnay nafas ko khuwahish say roka hoga
  79,41,To uska thikana janat hi hay
  79,42,Log ap say qiyamat kay waqay honay ka waqat daryafat kerty hein
  79,43,Ap ko is kay biyan kernay say kiaya taaluq
  79,44,Isskay ilam ki inteha to Allah ki janib hay
  79,45,Ap to sirf issy derty rahney walon ko agha kernay walay hein
  79,46,Jis roz ye ussay dekh lein gay to asa malom hoga kay sirf din ka akhiri hisa ya awal hisa hi(duniya mein)rahy hein